" ar gyfer <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=Thunderbird\">Thunderbird</a> neu'r <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=Calendar\">Calendr</a>."

